1. Hospitals or management institutions establish a database of statistical indicators for basic operation and medical and nursing services;
2. The hospital or management institution shall establish a medical and nursing business index system;
Specify that departments or personnel are responsible for regularly reviewing, monitoring, analyzing, and improving medical quality and safety management.

1. The hospital or management institution shall establish an information security protection system and have a disaster prevention and backup system;
2. The hospital has measures such as the implementation of information system operation authority control (including database and operation system);
3. The hospital or management organization has anti-virus, anti-intrusion measures and emergency (such as system paralysis) treatment plan and organizes drills.
